short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get AliExpress Invoice from order details as a printable PDF file

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Converts AliExpress order details into an invoice ready to print.

After installing the extension, you need to enter your details. 
  1. Click on the AliInfinity  icon.
  2.Go to order page
  3. And you will got the option to print or download the invoice.

 Free AliExpress Invoice Generator tool helps you to download your AliExpress invoices.

On AliExpress, VAT invoice is not automatic as the laws and tax rules differ from country to country. Our invoice generator tool allows you to generate a printful PDF file of your order, helping you justify your costs.

▬▬▬▬▬ FAQ ▬▬▬▬▬
Is AliInfinity  safe?
Yes. AliInfinity is a safe invoice making tool.

Is it aliexpress free invoice extension?
It is a Freemium aliexpress invoice extension. You can download unlimited invoices with it.
